## UX.3 Dependency

Restricted/confidential fields require **REPORT DESIGNER UX.3** governance unlock, which needs:
- Template type restrictions (`allowedTemplateTypes`)
- RBAC permission check (`requiredPermission`)
- Output mode restrictions (`allowedOutputModes`)
- Audit logging for sensitive field access
- Management approval flow for sensitive template publishing
